                    <span>This writing was quite interesting.  Dr. King as we all know was a great man and leader.  In this writing he points out a great way to look at the world, and all human beings within this world.  Throughout this writing he speaks of God and how God is the way.  A very enlightening piece of reading.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Cross Cultural</div>
